{"tid":1161063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「沒看到我排隊嗎！」 男不滿遭插隊 怒推女子頭","createTime":"2019-05-19T01:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T02:53:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4c14e5dccf6a8eab32592e7b2f43e9578335a0","tid":1161063,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-sZv8x4rMWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-sZv8x4rMWM&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=2086a080\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-sZv8x4rMWM</a><br />\n<br />\n不少人對「插隊」這個行為，相當感冒，<span style=\"color: red;\">新北</span>市一名男子，到超商買菸，不滿遭女子插隊，當場破口大罵，還出手推打女子的頭部，女子事後到醫院驗傷提告傷害，我們也訪問到這名推打人的男子，他喊冤說，當時為了讓其他顧客可以行走，他刻意空出走道，排隊排很久了，不滿女子一進超商就插隊，才會動手。"},{"pid":"0a413f65810a8736cc426e8106ff1db11f841e94","tid":1161063,"uid":7355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962713f1f3f688aa8a04ff4940c590e1a870a8b8","tid":1161063,"uid":99421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:11:54.000Z","msg":"新北+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1059320d59470483915c2c7e808c4884b6a1fece","tid":1161063,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"女插隊，男應該插她雞掰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d53e42261636bf84c382b29e7083e1f4445647a","tid":1161063,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"台狗d隊 企到好疏  扮鬼佬笑死人<br />\n<br />\n學下香港人排隊 痴到實一實  獅子山精神"},{"pid":"f92dbd6b3d1ec6fe5165be1d555de75bcea23e30","tid":1161063,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"打人有錯三小"},{"pid":"5ea7b6dbbf58d56db4874833a05363e496971dff","tid":1161063,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike